self.setUpClass()
num_qubits = 3
p = ql.Program('test_unitary_called_hadamard', platform, num_qubits)
k = ql.Kernel('akernel', platform, num_qubits)
u = ql.Unitary('hadamard', [complex(1.0, 0.0), complex(0.0, 0.0), complex(
    0.0, 0.0), complex(0.0, 1.0)])
u.decompose()
k.gate(u, [2])
p.add_kernel(k)
p.compile()
